description: Price Is Artificially Low To Offset Amazon Fixed Per-Item ShippingShare your music over a second pair of earphones with this premium quality Y-cable splitter. This Y-cable is compatible with all standard headphone jacks on devices such as MP3 players, iPods/iPhones (except Gen 3 Shuffle), portable media players, cell phones, notebook/netbook computers, and desktop computers.Contemporarily styled, this Y-cable splitter has the look that coordinates well with modern electronics. Why buy a Y-cable that looks like it was made in the 80's when you can have this sleek and stylish cable instead. Built with high quality materials, this Y-cable features durable metal barrel connectors and gold plated contacts for superior durability. The low profile connector is compatible with all standard headphone jacks, even ones that are recessed. Premium quality wiring with soft and supple wire jacket ensures long lasting tangle-free operation without breaking or fraying.Note: this item comes in bulk/oem packaging
title: Micca Premium Earphone and Headphone Splitter 3.5mm Y-Cable for MP3 Players, iPods, Computers
